title: Scenic Landscape
description: A picturesque landscape featuring rolling hills in the background, dotted with trees. The foreground shows a grassy field with a solitary tree, under a clear blue sky. The scene conveys a sense of tranquility and natural beauty.

title: Snow-Capped Mountains
description: A breathtaking view of snow-capped mountains under a partly cloudy sky. The peaks are rugged and steep, with a prominent mountain in the center that rises sharply against the backdrop of the sky. The foreground features rolling snow-covered slopes, creating a dramatic contrast with the blue sky.

title: Cows in a Pasture
description: A serene landscape featuring a group of cows resting in a green pasture. The scene includes a mix of brown and black-and-white cows, with some lying down and others standing. In the background, there are lush green fields and trees under a partly cloudy sky.
